overview: City Green Cars in West London is a premier Eco-friendly minicab service based in Chiswick, with an impressive fleet of Green vehicles. Enjoy our affordable, friendly and efficient transport service in and around London. Enjoy your journey in the UK with the lowest carbon emissions and low carbon footprint. Join us in safeguarding the environment and ensuring a better tomorrow! City Green Cars is an executive minicab company that is more than just a Green car service. CGC utilize the latest in car tracking technology and we are able to track your vehicle in real time on Google Maps. This ensures that we are always aware of the location of your vehicle and can assure you that you will be picked up on time and arrive at your destination in the most efficient manner. What makes our minicab service rise above that of our competitors is that we are a Green transport service provider. Our cars emit extremely low CO2 emissions, are 2013 models, and boast the highest specifications. As a passenger in one of our vehicles you can enjoy the comfort and luxury of a top spec vehicle while being kind to the environment. Saloon cars make an ideal solution for most commuters including business executives. They offer space and comfort while boasting great Eco-credentials.
